# Add a work entry

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Begin by navigating to `Entries > Work` and click the `New entry` button.
##### Hint: You can also click the arrow on the `New entry` button to select which Structure or Channel to add an Entry into.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

`Entries > Structure > Work` entries differ from `Entries > Structure > Pages`, as they have an extra tab, named `Thumbnail`. This is where you set up the thumbnail properties for that work item, which gets rendered when you add a `Structure` or `Thumbnail` to you `Row(s)` on a `Page` under `Entries > Pages`

